<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>ANTILOCK BRAKES/TRACTION CONTROL: BENDIX - TROUBLESHOOTING - 2000, 4000 &#38; 8000 MODELS - TROUBLESHOOTING
        - CHECKING NON-ELECTRICAL CAUSES
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="0">
        <title>CHECKING NON-ELECTRICAL CAUSES</title>
        <table id="t0403315" tblwidth="full-page" frame="all" numbered="no" view="reveal">
            <title>Checking Non-Electrical Causes</title>
            <tgroup cols="6" colsep="1" rowsep="1" align="center" charoff="50">
                <colspec colname="1" charoff="50" char="c" colwidth="0.83in"/>
                <colspec colname="2" charoff="50" char="c" colwidth="0.78in"/>
                <colspec colname="3" charoff="50" char="c" colwidth="1.62in"/>
                <colspec colname="4" charoff="50" char="c" colwidth="0.91in"/>
                <colspec colname="5" charoff="50" char="c" colwidth="0.94in"/>
                <colspec colname="6" charoff="50" char="c" colwidth="1.62in"/>
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>STEP</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>KEY</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>ACTION</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>SPEC.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>YES / IN SPEC.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6">
                            <para>NO / OUT OF SPEC.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody valign="top">
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Check Exciter Ring/Wheel Sensor for: 1. Runout between the sensor and the exciter ring
                                (.025 in. max.) and 2. Exciter ring should be free of damage and mounted properly.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Correct defects noted and rerun
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_7.xml" xrefid="t0403301">INITIAL START-UP TEST
                                    PROCEDURE</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Refer to the appropriate Service Manual Section and verify the wheel bearing end play
                                is not more than .005 inch.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Correct defects noted and rerun
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_7.xml" xrefid="t0403301">INITIAL START-UP TEST
                                    PROCEDURE</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>3.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Check for: 1. Dragging brakes, 2. Trapped air in actuator, 3. Out of round brake
                                drums, 4. Faulty return springs, 5. Parking brake system faults.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Correct defects noted and rerun
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_7.xml" xrefid="t0403301">INITIAL START-UP TEST
                                    PROCEDURE</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Disconnect and connect connectors at controller, modulators and sensors. Do magnetic
                                reset and note condition of LEDs. Are RED LEDs ON?
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="center">
                            <para>RED LEDs ON.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to ,
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_9.xml" xrefid="t0403303">INSPECTION FOR ILLUMINATED LEDS, PART
                                    A</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Correct defects noted and rerun
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_7.xml" xrefid="t0403301">INITIAL START-UP TEST
                                    PROCEDURE</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
